    <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
        <body>


            <div xml:id="Aink403">
                <lg type="edition">
                    <l> puṇarntakā taliyiṟ putalvaṉ ṟalaiyu</l>
                    <l>mamarnta vuḷḷam peritā kiṉṟē</l>
                    <l>yakaṉperuñ ciṟappiṟ ṟantai peyaraṉ</l>
                    <l>muṟuvali ṉiṉṉakai payiṟṟic </l>
                    <l>ciṟutē ruruṭṭun taḷarnaṭai kaṇṭē.</l>
                </lg>
                <p type="translation" xml:lang="en">
                    [The hero's] heart, which dwelled in the son of his beloved with whom he has
                    already united, swelled, seeing the shaky steps of the boy with [the hero's]
                    very greatly esteemed father's name, sweetly smiling a toothy smile and rolling
                    around his toy chariot.
                </p>
            </div>
